ExamNext DataBase Design :-

âœ… First Understand System Flow (VERY IMPORTANT)

Your system has 3 actors:

ğŸ‘‰ Admin
ğŸ‘‰ Teacher
ğŸ‘‰ Student

Admin â†’ Manage Users
Teacher â†’ Create Exam â†’ Add Questions â†’ Publish Exam
Student â†’ Attempt Exam â†’ Result Generated

RoleTbl
UserTbl
ExamTbl
QuestionTbl
ExamAssignTbl
